text:
Adding one more vegetable dish to every meal... or maybe
Reducing the frequency of snacks...?

We tend to buy "new" or "limited edition" stuff
Without even thinking twice, so I'll try to avoid that...!

When it comes to large dishes...
I'll try to resist taking another bite a few times...

Good work.
What were you talking about? It seemed quite serious...

It's more like restraint, you know, So the
glutton in me can't help but look a bit disappointed!

Oh, uh...
I brought some snacks as a treat...
